print.io.photosource

Interface PhotoSourceNavigator<S extends PhotoSource>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - Type of the PhotoSource used by this navigator.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPhotoSourceNavigator

    public interface PhotoSourceNavigator<S extends PhotoSource>
    An interface of photo source navigator used to navigate within photo source on the screen.
    Author:
    Vlado
